# Demo videos — all compressed to *-web.mp4 (0.9–5MB each) and self-hosted.
# Raw originals stay excluded: bite-balance.mp4 (174MB) and
# algo-visualizer.mp4 (109MB) exceed GitHub's 100MB limit.
# All *-web.mp4 versions are allow-listed.
assets/videos/*.mp4
!assets/videos/*-web.mp4

